ERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=611e15c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20130324%2FPLFB3D2RDOC3J2XBG5ILDJCE7E%2F&h=77d19a96\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20130324/PLFB3D2RDOC3J2XBG5ILDJCE7E/</a><br />\n<br />\n所羅門王嘅審判，呢種假祖國你要埋我嗰份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:34:18.000Z","msg":"矮仔其實只係拋，扮完全唔在乎整死香港，唔怕出兵搶返香港，主權第一。<br />\n<br />\n唔係港資先入去，啲外資跟住入去，會咁易信佢改革開放？之前幾十年輸出革命又攪政治運動，令亞洲地區無日安寧，仲同大佬蘇聯反臉，差啲打核戰。<br />\n<br />\n出兵攞返香港，唔怕一窮二白。都啱，不過文革之後支那已經乜都無，外匯都無晒咁滯，剛剛有返外交，人哋可以反面同返台灣建交，日本可以即時中止援助，連軍隊都亂到七彩。<br />\n<br />\n佢無講錯香港唔係金蛋，只係支共吊命草嚟。"},{"pid":"b67b70a7c150ffcd7fb84855516bc443ed7a4ab9","tid":2439031,"uid":270390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:47:50.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"35a399fea521c6c04ba05582653ae73cd23ffd9f","tid":2439031,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11925b98cbb1324240bdecbae78b849ec14b00e6","tid":2439031,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:10:45.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那狗賤種又害香港"},{"pid":"f75976122217bedac53d387d39cbb9c7ade9850b","tid":2439031,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:13:35.000Z","msg":"出解放軍，英國頂唔頂到先"},{"pid":"9cd905eeef3885e69827b61e16e4f040adc7ebde","tid":2439031,"uid":282855,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:16:14.000Z","msg":"韓